reventable death globally and is addictive the companys operations and its competitors are highly controversial and are increasingly the subject of litigation and restrictive legislation from governments concerned about the health impacts of its products philip morris was a longterm main sponsor of the scuderia ferrari formula one team until  and continues its association with the team as of  albeit on a more lowkey basis and without overt advertising contents  history  brands  board of directors  research  controversies and public health disputes  australia  norway  uruguay  united kingdom  other  sponsorship  philip morris sports  references  external links historyedit the company states its history is traced to a london tobacconists philip morris’s  opening of a single shop on london’s bond street which sold tobacco and cigarettes the current operations center of the company is located in lausanne switzerland it owns  of the top  tobacco brands in the world in april  philip morris announced that it would close its moorabbin plant in australia by the end of  after operating for  years due to the gradual decline of sales in the last ten years and difficulties conforming to  australian government regulation about reducing fire risks in  it sold  billion cigarettes brandsedit philip morris factory in russia philip morris international has six multibillion us brands including  dji sam soe  was launched on  and is a brand of kretek cigarettes it is the best seller of kretek cigarettes in indonesia  lm was launched by liggett  myers on  with tagline american cigarettes of the highest quality with the best filter lm variants include full flavor shorts full flavor s lights ultra lights menthol shorts menthol s menthol light shorts menthol light s turkish blend shorts turkish blend s and lm mild kretek  longbeach include on australia and indonesia on  longbeach variant include longbeach filter and longbeach mild  marlboro was launched on  marlboro is the premium brand marl