arch  controversies and public health disputes  australia  norway  uruguay  united kingdom  other  sponsorship  philip morris sports  references  external links historyedit the company states its history is traced to a london tobacconists philip morris’s  opening of a single shop on london’s bond street which sold tobacco and cigarettes the current operations center of the company is located in lausanne switzerland it owns  of the top  tobacco brands in the world in april  philip morris announced that it would close its moorabbin plant in australia by the end of  after operating for  years due to the gradual decline of sales in the last ten years and difficulties conforming to  australian government regulation about reducing fire risks in  it sold  billion cigarettes brandsedit philip morris factory in russia philip morris international has six multibillion us brands including  dji sam soe  was launched on  and is a brand of kretek cigarettes it is the best seller of kretek cigarettes in indonesia  lm was launched by liggett  myers on  with tagline american cigarettes of the highest quality with the best filter lm variants include full flavor shorts full flavor s lights ultra lights menthol shorts menthol s menthol light shorts menthol light s turkish blend shorts turkish blend s and lm mild kretek  longbeach include on australia and indonesia on  longbeach variant include longbeach filter and longbeach mild  marlboro was launched on  marlboro is the premium brand marlboro variants include marlboro special marlboro menthol marlboro lights marlboro lights menthol marlboro mix filter kretek marlboro flavor plus marlboro black menthol and heatsticks a heated tobacco product  st dupont paris is the brand cigarette designed by simon tissot dupont on  with the black packaging st dupont paris variants include filter lights menthol and menthol lights  u mild was launched on indonesia on may   after indonesian revolution u mild is a mild kretek cigarette sold in indonesia it