h a new center for heets in dresden in addition the company will also convert its cigarette facilities in russia and greece by the close of  it intends to have a total yearly installed capacity of around  billion heated tobacco segments heets and iqos have been accessible in  towns throughout romania from the start of this year iqos is presently accessible in major cities in over  markets across the world and is anticipated to be accessible in  markets either major cities or countrywide by the close of  as capacity allows commenting on this update andré calantzopoulos the ceo of philip morris reported that their investment in romania further exhibits their commitment to an imminent period in which smokefree offerings ultimately replace cigarettes they are thrilled the  million smokers across the globe who have already left smoking and moved to iqos the company anticipate this momentum to continue and the transformation of the romanian facility will assist them to meet the increasing demand from adult smokers for better options to cigarettes trendingadvertise here most disruptive biotech vbiohttpwwwfinancialstrendcomdisruptive biotech vbio decodes targeted drug delivery for stem cellstop stock analysis at journal transcripthttpwwwjournaltranscriptcomearly bird alerts on the hottest otc companieswall street pr  big buyout opportunityhttpwallstreetprcomhere’s how to leverage this breakthrough technology…enter the  cannabis markethttpwwwfinancialstrendcomvbio cannabis industry setup for explosive growth tweet tagsnysepmphilip morris international incphilip morris international inc nysepm jon slotnick related posts viewsbusinessjuly   philip morris international inc nysepm q  diluted eps at  viewsbusinessjuly   why philip morris international inc nysepm is in focusphilip morris international inc nysepm increases outlay in heated tobacco unit facility symbol        alert        high        gain     vbio                          imlff                        cmxc           